  1→//! Local LLM provider with pluggable backends.
  2→//!
  3→//! Supports multiple inference backends:
  4→//! - GGUF (llama.cpp) - Cross-platform, CPU + GPU
  5→//! - MLX - Apple Silicon optimized (macOS only)
  6→//!
  7→//! The provider automatically selects the best backend based on the platform
  8→//! and available hardware.
